# Input

```js
let [a,b]=c;
let [d,...e]=c;
let [aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa,bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb,...cccccccccccccccccccccccccccccc]=f;

```


# Formatted

```js
let [a, b] = c;
let [d, ...e] = c;
let [
	aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa,
	bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb,
	...cccccccccccccccccccccccccccccc
] = f;

```
